message: Phase 0 deliverables are EXCEPTIONALLY COMPREHENSIVE. All 4 expected deliverables fully met: (1) Complete 11-week mapping with date ranges and PDF sources, (2) Detailed key concepts/theories/researchers extracted per week, (3) Learning objectives documented for all weeks, (4) Assessment structure accurately documented (2 midterms 30% each, final 40%). Master document (PHASE1_COURSE_STRUCTURE_COMPREHENSIVE_MAPPING.md) is 957 lines of highly detailed content. Individual week analyses show excellent depth with structured JSON format matching target schema.
